{"tid":294411,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鐘意唱歌但唱得唔得聽","createTime":"2017-06-23T02:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T10:07:40.000Z","uid":92132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20ddbb23aff312eb73c77b92a631e9bf5e4245d4","tid":294411,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:57:14.000Z","msg":"自問我好鐘意唱歌<br />\n一黎可以發洩<br />\n二黎可以減壓<br />\n三黎好鐘意唱出口 <br />\n但係屋企人又覺得我好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己都有上網睇過D學唱歌既方法<br />\n乜野腹式呼吸 低喉頭 打喊路黎開聲 放鬆頸部 肚用力HOLD 住  唔好大聲叫歌<br />\n全部都有研究過<br />\n但有時錄低自己把聲又覺得唔好聽 <br />\n唔知道方法用得岩唔岩<br />\n同埋好唔穩定 <br />\n曾經唱K 有人話我唱得好聽<br />\n但係 可能係我狀態好 一差就直頭想收聲唔唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟唱歌有咩野一定要做既PRINCIPLE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9a12c8f8979af7e145c5c76ee84f93504fe4c0","tid":294411,"uid":111849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"搵個老師學啦<br />\n你共嗚都未識 唱乜野歌<br />\n仲要做音準 拍子 擴大音域之類訓練<br />\n無老師睇住你唱錯哂都唔知"},{"pid":"6d9394b6b24563b3c734f4f5b33872bef18cf112","tid":294411,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵個老師學啦<br />\n你共嗚都未識 唱乜野歌<br />\n仲要做音準 拍子 擴大音域之類訓練<br />\n無老師睇住你唱錯哂都唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都岩既<br />\n都好想搵個老師學唱歌<br />\n巴打有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cf1f166556d5c5f80a358819f9c7733a32d0b1","tid":294411,"uid":37795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:30:21.000Z","msg":"剩係講發聲方面:<br />\n<br />\n1) support: 學識點樣呼吸, 邊度用力, 邊度要放鬆<br />\n2) 氣流: 控制比到合適既氣流同要流暢<br />\n3) 母音: 根據音高同想要既效果, 用合適既母音"},{"pid":"26b887de18de8995812235a5f3d9bd2afceb1ac9","tid":294411,"uid":19300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"same<br />\n乜鳩都鍾意唱一餐<br />\n張學友到death metal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣都係搵左勁多教學<br />\n由五音不全練到起碼唱到一兩句啱音<br />\n不過我唔求唱得好<br />\n自己唱得開心就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136088703b8e6e420877d8495fb2eeec867a3ee3","tid":294411,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same<br />\n乜鳩都鍾意唱一餐<br />\n張學友到death metal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣都係搵左勁多教學<br />\n由五音不全練到起碼唱到一兩句啱音<br />\n不過我唔求唱得好<br />\n自己唱得開心就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死腔點練"},{"pid":"41238b4b1218c1fd3b92b7c82e4ab022779a954f","tid":294411,"uid":19300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>same<br />\n乜鳩都鍾意唱一餐<br />\n張學友到death metal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣都係搵左勁多教學<br />\n由五音不全練到起碼唱到一兩句啱音<br />\n不過我唔求唱得好<br />\n自己唱得開心就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死腔點練</blockquote><br />\n唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扮下就算"},{"pid":"bc1cd8150efe192a852ae2c83f98114ade85f8e6","tid":294411,"uid":10141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"Same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近想買支咪錄自己唱歌<br />\n但係一諗到唱歌咁難聽，就覺得好似好曬錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da3ab51986c8646b9c614ee87aca228a29acce9","tid":294411,"uid":116360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剩係講發聲方面:<br />\n<br />\n1) support: 學識點樣呼吸, 邊度用力, 邊度要放鬆<br />\n2) 氣流: 控制比到合適既氣流同要流暢<br />\n3) 母音: 根據音高同想要既效果, 用合適既母音</blockquote><br />\n講到母音我就不其然諗到美聲~ 雖然我知道咩歌都要母音純正 不過講到母音真係好聲樂feel"},{"pid":"ad2123c5abf6603bdcc5ac78416d58d0f8481bee","tid":294411,"uid":37795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剩係講發聲方面:<br />\n<br />\n1) support: 學識點樣呼吸, 邊度用力, 邊度要放鬆<br />\n2) 氣流: 控制比到合適既氣流同要流暢<br />\n3) 母音: 根據音高同想要既效果, 用合適既母音</blockquote><br />\n講到母音我就不其然諗到美聲~ 雖然我知道咩歌都要母音純正 不過講到母音真係好聲樂feel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傳統美聲又好, 唱流行曲又好, 講野都好 都關母音事架, 因為唱的字就係 子音+母音, 傳統美聲因為定左一定要某的效果所以對母音既要求好嚴緊, 唱流行曲就可以自由發揮好多, 但係為左有效率咁發聲都需要注意母音既運用"},{"pid":"73231444db0a3f311fa340633682c3718165b6ae","tid":294411,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:13:42.000Z","msg":"咩係唔得聽？"},{"pid":"e86c85459ec1c068a7ef1fbd4766caece8f2ea4b","tid":294411,"uid":92132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩係唔得聽？</blockquote><br />\n打錯左 <br />\n應該係唔好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadac72983ad02292d2b0280f8d60b238c2221df","tid":294411,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:48:29.000Z","msg":"大家點睇 dear jane 首 一去不返 <br />\n高音到痴線 但好鐘意唱呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be37f696c0ffa2db082a1ec551de6985cb3ac197","tid":294411,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家點睇 dear jane 首 一去不返 <br />\n高音到痴線 但好鐘意唱呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDJ啲歌都唔係好高音姐"},{"pid":"cb6732fbd223f3a1023f283f00dd1925d440ce40","tid":294411,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:02:11.000Z